reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 27, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I love the colors. The quality, flexibility, versatility & sizes of them. They're easy to use & easy to clean.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fantastic set of cookware utensils
reviews.reviewText: Every piece in this set is useful and functional. I wasn’t sure about the whisk so I ordered a silicone whisk separately when I ordered this set. Although the whisk with the set is covered with silicone so it won’t scratch cookware. The holder contains all of the pieces but they’re a little tight. I intended to put them in a drawer anyhow so if you do plan on using the counter top jar, maybe put only the essentials in there. My old nylon set were starting to flake and warp. I’m hoping this set lasts me many years. I might get my sister a set for her kitchen as a gift.** these are on the smaller side. The spoons are not deep and the ladle is small. Some of the spatulas and other items are about 6” long. Still happy but wish they were larger/deeper.

This is a really nice set of utensils, and feel like they will last a good long time. I saw this same set on another well known home goods website for $93.00 on sale from $104! The colour is a lovely teal blue and I like the fact that the holder does not have anything written on it.
Love these! Not only do they look good on the countertop, there was a lot of useful utensils in there and great price for them all.

reviews.reviewTitle: Chief is cooking in the kitchen
reviews.reviewText: I bought these silicone cooking utensils for my new apartment and they work fantastic! I am super lazy when it comes to cleaning so I love that you just throw these bad boys into the dishwasher and they come out perfectly clean. I haven't had any issues with these melting and they come into contact with a lot of heat. I've seen a few other people say that the whisk breaks but I just put it in handle side down and I haven't had any problems. I also love how it comes with a container and I like the color.

reviews.reviewTitle: Ne fond pas à la chaleur
reviews.reviewText: Cela m'a pris du temps à sélectionner l'ensemble que je voulais. Finalement, je suis satisfaite de celui-ci. J'ai seulement dû acheter une spatule à crêpes supplémentaire pour compléter le tout. Ha, et on ne met pas tout dans le pot, seulement les plus essentiels.
